Key Features of the Arattai App
This application offers many useful features to compete with popular messaging apps like WhatsApp and Telegram. 

Here are some key points:
‚Ä¢	It can send text messages instantly with your friends and family.
‚Ä¢	This application is providing High-quality voice and video calling options for its users. For group chats also this feature is available.
‚Ä¢	Its users can also create groups to share messages, photos, and videos with multiple people at a time.
‚Ä¢	Users can also share photos, videos, documents, and other files easily upto 100MB.
‚Ä¢	This app stores the data securely within India and does not shares it with third parties.
‚Ä¢	Lightweight: This is designed in a such way to work well on low-end devices and also for slow internet connections.
‚Ä¢	No Ads: Everyone can enjoy an ad-free messaging experience chats without any disturbance.
These features make this application more attractive for people who want communication without compromising on privacy.
